{"tid":373200,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「戒丁」 適當戒色 有效提升專注力，創意，體力，異性吸引力","createTime":"2017-08-25T00:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T05:16:11.000Z","uid":123335,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d60f315bec31929c52a5015d44b40c34d9ac4579","tid":373200,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"咩叫適當戒色？<br />\n量化解釋，就係最多每星期1次 <br />\n唔止係打丁，連性交都計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n根據醫師林瀛洲說「禁欲時體內睪固酮濃度高，會增加體能爆發力」<br />\n睪固酮係人體分泌的壓力荷爾蒙<br />\n它刺激肌肉、骨骼、皮膚、性器官等發展。<br />\n睪固酮引發肌肉的增加、性器官的生長、骨骼的形成、更低沉的聲音，以及更旺盛的活力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://roguehealthandfitness.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/testosterone-molecules-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Froguehealthandfitness.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Ftestosterone-molecules-1.jpg&h=4896caaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://herbolab.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Normal-Testosterone.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fherbolab.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FNormal-Testosterone.jpg&h=7b1079f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為男人每射一次精，都會好傷元氣<br />\n會令男性體內既睪固酮含量下降<br />\n要抖最少要三日先可以回復元氣<br />\n要提升回復返男性體內既睪固酮含量，<br />\n林醫師說「運動可以提升睪固酮」<br />\n<br />\n小弟建議5天工作周打工仔既大家<br />\n可考慮星期五晚做約囡囡做性事／睇AV打丁抒發下壓力<br />\n然後星期六，日出下街，做下運動，訓好，食好，休息夠<br />\n以作回復完美體態，逐步回升精神, 專注力, 精力, 活力, 吸引力, 魅力 <br />\n以提升星期一至五既工作表現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n形成一個良性循環 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d829c6de0e37f19e1eef35ffd5dd6437834ad4a7","tid":373200,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:38:33.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12659241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F12659241&d=L4AMZ6LbyX1Qs6BI5eXwoUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=dc119d08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12659241</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>Abstract</ins><br />\nThe purpose of this study is to gain understanding of the relationship between ejaculation and serum testosterone level in men. The serum testosterone concentrations of 28 volunteers were investigated daily during abstinence periods after ejaculation for two phases. The authors found that the fluctuations of testosterone levels from the 2nd to 5th day of abstinence were minimal. <span style=\"color: red;\"><em><ins>On the 7th day of abstinence, however, a clear peak of serum testosterone appeared, reaching 145.7% of the baseline ( P &lt; 0.01).</ins></em></span> No regular fluctuation was observed following continuous abstinence after the peak. Ejaculation is the precondition and beginning of the special periodic serum testosterone level variations, which would not occur without ejaculation. <span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>The results showed that ejaculation-caused variations were characterized by a peak on the 7th day of abstinence</ins></span>; and that the effective time of an ejaculation is 7 days minimum. These data are the first to document the phenomenon of the periodic change in serum testosterone level; the correlation between ejaculation and periodic change in the serum testosterone level, and the pattern and characteristics of the periodic change.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翻譯: <br />\n- 禁慾7日後, 睪固酮會上升<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>+45.7% </ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fe684b61dc678093ead93559293f1998a3029ac5","tid":373200,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cab173be6bd5408a24bc7d20e484bbc6ff3d67","tid":373200,"uid":8561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:46:28.000Z","msg":"周大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bf74a88cc34a48d568311849a47ba8631dc43f","tid":373200,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T00:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實又唔洗話要戒色戒一, 兩年 or 戒到永遠 <br />\n西方研究指出，只要戒 7 日<br />\n對男人好重要，提升活力同各方面機能既睪固酮<br />\n就已經會上升 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>+ 45.7% </ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟建議, 以往有性沉溺既巴打, e.g. 每日1次／隔日1次<br />\n俾個數自己，戒7日<br />\n一嘗睪固酮上升 + 4成半既感覺<br />\n試完再決定會唔會長遠地管理自己既性活動, 包括同女扑野 / 打丁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5956b6eeab401c2cf214fc89fb1c607766ebde2e","tid":373200,"uid":80633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"有說服力，高質過一般戒丁post"},{"pid":"e6fbb0f92b37cfeea5d7226a7f28f1429c321f30","tid":373200,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"學術台係咪平時都係咁靜"},{"pid":"7d96ff74f665b9e87f1da4ce3060ba2b07cd5dd5","tid":373200,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34781cf7bc723772c228a1916a673c04e3118710","tid":373200,"uid":127347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有說服力，高質過一般戒丁post</blockquote><br />\nAgger</blockquote><br />\n係，好過果啲話唔好打j既post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4baad3f0c26dd1061976097fb688d8089667e4b","tid":373200,"uid":52287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T01:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no